    "Even if the EU legislator intends to keep the current framework-where risk categories are pre-determined based on the AI's scopes -this model can aid in the proposed additional assessments that could revise the risk categorisation (i.e., risk significance).",
    "However, what we have presented in this section, is just a general framework.",
